column4: The Yellow House by Sarah M. Broom

column6: Using GoodReads as a proxy for subjective quality, it's 4.1, 4.47, 4.54, 4.18 and 4.44. So, giving Yellow House (A) and Heartbeat (D) 15% combined. Adding 5% to the default of 20% to B, C, E for 25% each, with 10% remaining. If we use number of GoodReads reviews as a proxy for popularity, B stands out as having 5 times the number of reviews. Adding 5% there.
